						<div class="postbody">PRG R/W and /ROMSEL are low for writes to $8000-FFFF which is what you're trying to detect.  You're not &quot;inverting them to make it work&quot;, you're sensing them as low which is what you care about for your condition.<br /><br />IDK much about the powerpak, but based on what thefox explained with the M2 inverter I would ignore that statement about all signals active high because it's simply not true.</div>

					
